FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777246395
OL,3,CBritish reluctance to talk about death
OL,4,Ccosting bereaved #157m a year ` survey
OL,6,FAmong respondents who had arranged a
OL,7,Ffuneral, 54% said they were uncertain
OL,8,Fabout key decisions because no
OL,9,Fconversations had taken place
OL,10,Fbeforehand.
OL,12,FAlmost three in 10 who arranged a
OL,13,Ffuneral (29%) felt anxiety at the lack
OL,14,Fof clarity, while 22% experienced
OL,15,Fguilt, worrying they had made the
OL,16,Fwrong choices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
