PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777246395
OL,3,CBritish reluctance to talk about death
OL,4,Ccosting bereaved #157m a year ` survey
OL,6,F"Our research shows 24% of people who
OL,7,Fhave been bereaved in the past five
OL,8,Fyears have never discussed their end-
OL,9,Fof-life wishes, and as a result,
OL,10,Fgrieving families are left to make
OL,11,Femotionally charged and often
OL,12,Fexpensive decisions.
OL,14,F"Talking about what you want at the
OL,15,Fend of your life is one of the
OL,16,Fkindest, most practical gifts you can
OL,17,Fgive the people you love."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
